Nigerian musicians, Falz and Teni have left fans blushing after a video of the duo in romantic gesture surfaced. Teni and Falz Singer Teni and lawyer turned singer, Folarin Falana, popularly known as Falz have shared a video with Falz confessing his love for Teni. In the video, Falz could be heard saying: “Teni I have so much feeling for you” Teni who blushed, him for a kiss and another one, which he willing obliged… ‘Kiss so smooth!!!’, she captioned the video. The video has left a smile on the faces of their fans. Source